2007-03-13  Thomas Vander Stichele  <thomas at apestaart dot org>

	* flumotion/common/common.py:
	* flumotion/test/test_common.py:
	  add optional fractional argument to formatTime
	* flumotion/component/base/admin_gtk.py:
