2006-09-05  Michael Smith  <msmith@fluendo.com>

	* flumotion/component/feedcomponent010.py:
	* flumotion/manager/depgraph.py:
	* flumotion/test/test_manager_depgraph.py:
	* flumotion/test/test_manager_manager.py:
