	* flumotion/component/consumers/httpstreamer/resources.py
	(HTTPStreamingResource.logWrite): Log the already-parsed get
	parameters as well.

	* flumotion/twisted/integration.py (test): Sigh, it seems trial
	2.4 requires a timeout.

