	* flumotion/test/test_flavors.py: Refactored so as not to use
	unittest.deferredResult, avoids lots of nasty warnings with
	twisted 2.2.

	* flumotion/manager/manager.py (Vishnu.setConnectionInfo): Change
	using_ssl to use_ssl.

